snippet.title: LogosQuiz
snippet.description:
More than 30.000.000 downloads around the world! Thank you!

LogosQuiz is a game full of fun that consists on guessing the names of hundreds of logos from different companies. To achieve this you have a lot of clues which you can use to help you complete the game. You can also ask your friends if you don't know the answer! Challenge them to see who know more logos!

MORE THAN 1.000 BRANDS!
We are continuously surrounded by company logos, we can see them on TV, walking on the street, at important events... everywhere! But, how many of them can you recognize just seeing part of the logo?

HINTS
If you are blocked and you don't know the answer for a logo, don't give up! Use one of the hints that each logo has! You will learn a lot of interesting facts about companies or organizations.

ASK YOUR FRIENDS
If after using all the hints, you still don't know the answer, don't worry! You can always ask your friends through twitter or Facebook, and complete the missing ones with them!

GAME STATS
See how many hits, how many misses and how many close ups questions. Check your total score and share it on Facebook or twitter. Compete with your friends!
